title: Grand Theft Auto Vice City Stories Soundtrack
description:
(I had to reupload, because i named it wrong first time.)


So this is it. I wanted to do that for a long time, and finally it came to an end.
The Vice City Storyes radio stations, including VCPR, wanted by so many in mp3 format, are here for the masses. Enjoy :). And coment. And SEED!!! I will seed for as long as i can, but i can't promise forever.

Note: the files are all in mp3 format, vbr, highest quality. ID3 tags are completed from Wikipedia. The game audio was captured by conecting PSP's line-out (headphones) to computer line in. So don't ask if i discovered an at3 to mp3 converter. Because i didn't.
